yes i know i already wrote in here today, but im becoming more of a loser day by day, so i dont really care. i am so surprised that i didnt get fired last night. my true inner bitchiness was definitely shining through. i snapped at everything that the dumbass chick said to me. it wasnt the usual snap, it was more like the "i dont fucking care", "why the fuck do you come to work if all you do is stand around and talk to the manager", haha and when she asked why she was working on the cleaning list and i wasnt she got a "ya know, you dont ever fucking do anything, why should I help YOU?" Yes i am a bitch and i am very fucking proud of it. i am sick and tired of people walking all over me, thats how ive been my whole life and well i guess this is where that is going to end, so fuck you all. i dont care anymore if i hurt people with my words. they hurt me all the time. they dont seem to care about how what they say and do or better yet, what they dont do has an impact on me. i always get stuck with the people that say they care about me, but they dont. they are all fucking liars. i hate everyone who has ever hurt me. youll get yours you stupid pieces of shit. i dont fucking care anymore. god, i am filled with rage. rage that has been there my whole life, but ive never said anything cause i was too god damn scared to hurt people, well im not fucking scared anymore. 

~KmC~
